[SN]TITLE[SN]
The schools swapping shoes for slippers

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Have you ever wanted to wear your slippers to school? Well, now some children across the UK can!

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Some primary schools have allowed their pupils to wear slippers in class after research suggested it helps them get better grades.
Pupils at this school say that they love wearing slippers, because they feel more relaxed, and some even think they're working better because of it.
These children in London told the BBC what they think about it too...
